=======================================================================
         OGLE Study of the Sagittarius Dwarf Spheroidal Galaxy
                    and its M54 Globular Cluster

  A. Hamanowicz, P. Pietrukowicz, A. Udalski, P. Mroz, I. Soszynski,
       M.K. Szymanski, J. Skowron, R. Poleski, L. Wyrzykowski,
